Create tokens on Sepolia ERC20, Solana SPL, and ICP ICRCs

Fund canister with all tokens from all chains
Update prices every 10 seconds
Allow to create limit orders on all chains
Allow to cancel limit orders on all chains
Allow to create market orders on all chains
Allow to create close position orders on all chains

Websockets to fetch prices and update orders
ICP will fetch prices from Websocket on ICP chain

Frontend displays prices from Websocket
if limit order hit target price, it will be executed on canister
if limit order hit target price, it will check if close position order is hit